      <title>警方在驱散令后拆除了加州大学洛杉矶分校的抗议营地</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/tensions-high-at-ucla-as-protesters-ordered-to-disperse</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前一天晚上与反抗议者发生暴力事件后，身着防暴装备的警察拆除了亲巴勒斯坦抗议者在洛杉矶加州大学搭建的路障和帐篷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/tensions-high-at-ucla-as-protesters-ordered-to-disperse</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 08:45:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
